Method Detail

getList

public List<Object> getList()
Provides a List> of values read from the list rows forms. The values are retrieved as beans of the class that was defined in the constructor. If the bean class was not defined in the constructor, the values are stored as map entries.

Returns:
List> with values (beans or maps) read from the form list rows forms.
